column1: ## Kevin: this file holds the raw data of the GROMACS measurements, for parsing with an external tool.
## 3 columns with nodes/procs/threads properties, then multiple Iterations results
## columns starting with '# ' define 1/ the experiment name 2/ the experiment properties in the following columns. These properties apply to the following rows until a new experiment is found
## columns startring with '##' are comments, so ignored for the parsing
